    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Ageratum panamense are skin infections, such as boils and abscesses, which are treated with its antiseptic properties. Ageratum panamense is also used to treat respiratory issues like bronchitis and asthma due to its anti-inflammatory compounds. Additionally, its antibacterial properties help heal wounds, including cuts and burns, by preventing infection. Its antifungal properties make it effective against fungal infections like ringworm and athlete's foot. Furthermore, Ageratum panamense's antipyretic properties reduce fever in cases of malaria, typhoid fever, and other infectious diseases.",
